WordLists

These modules are intended to provide an interface for working with
word lists for glossaries, coursebooks, etc. and simple dictionary
lookups.


INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install

SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the
perldoc command.

    perldoc WordLists::Base

You can also look for information at:

    RT, CPAN's request tracker
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=WordLists

    AnnoCPAN, Annotated CPAN documentation
        http://annocpan.org/dist/WordLists

    CPAN Ratings
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/WordLists

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/WordLists/


